    <item>
      <title>BlueCrest 未能阻止向投资者支付 7 亿美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-02/bluecrest-loses-court-bid-to-block-700-million-investor-payout</link>
      <description><![CDATA[迈克尔·普拉特 (Michael Platt) 的投资公司 BlueCrest Capital Management 在与英国金融监管机构的诉讼中败诉后，再次面临向投资者赔偿 7 亿美元的义务，原因是该公司在内部基金中偏袒员工。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-02/bluecrest-loses-court-bid-to-block-700-million-investor-payout</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 02 Oct 2024 13:36:55 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国码头工人罢工：衡量经济成本</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-10-02/us-dockworker-s-strike-measuring-the-economic-cost</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周二，美国东部和墨西哥湾沿岸各大港口的码头工人因未能就新合同达成一致而罢工，这是近 50 年来首次。彭博经济的 Anna Wong 在彭博电视台上分析了此次罢工对美国经济的潜在影响。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-10-02/us-dockworker-s-strike-measuring-the-economic-cost</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 02 Oct 2024 13:28:46 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>阿波罗首席执行官罗文警告称，美联储大幅降息可能会适得其反</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-02/apollo-ceo-rowan-warns-that-aggressive-rate-cuts-could-backfire</link>
      <description><![CDATA[阿波罗全球管理公司首席执行官马克·罗文表示，他认为美联储目前没有理由继续降息来刺激经济。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-02/apollo-ceo-rowan-warns-that-aggressive-rate-cuts-could-backfire</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 02 Oct 2024 13:18:44 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>全文：罗文谈私募市场贷款、选举、美联储</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-10-02/in-full-rowan-on-private-market-lending-election-fed-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[阿波罗全球管理公司首席执行官马克·罗文讨论了私募市场贷款、阿波罗与花旗集团合作后可能出现的更多银行合作以及私募股权与公募股权的前景。在与彭博社乔纳森·费罗的对话中，他还对美国总统大选和美联储政策前景发表了评论。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-10-02/in-full-rowan-on-private-market-lending-election-fed-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 02 Oct 2024 13:11:36 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>匈牙利央行在福林贬值后承诺实施“有限”绿色计划</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-02/hungarian-central-bank-pledges-limited-green-program-after-forint-drop</link>
      <description><![CDATA[匈牙利央行承诺维持“严谨而紧缩”的货币政策，以缓解投资者的担忧，因为福林跌至一年半以来的最低水平。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-02/hungarian-central-bank-pledges-limited-green-program-after-forint-drop</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 02 Oct 2024 13:08:25 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>法国计划在 2025 年削减 600 亿欧元支出并提高税收</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-02/france-plans-66-billion-in-spending-cuts-and-tax-hikes-in-2025</link>
      <description><![CDATA[法国总理米歇尔·巴尼耶 (Michel Barnier) 寻求收回不断扩大的预算赤字并增强投资者对法国的信心，该国计划明年削减约 600 亿欧元（664 亿美元）的支出并提高税收。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-02/france-plans-66-billion-in-spending-cuts-and-tax-hikes-in-2025</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 02 Oct 2024 11:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>以色列誓言对伊朗大规模导弹袭击进行报复</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-02/israel-vows-retaliation-for-massive-iranian-missile-attack</link>
      <description><![CDATA[伊朗向以色列发射了约 200 枚弹道导弹后，本杰明内塔尼亚胡誓言要对伊朗进行报复，世界大国担心这一重大升级可能升级为中东战争。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-02/israel-vows-retaliation-for-massive-iranian-missile-attack</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 02 Oct 2024 07:06:51 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
