      <title>关注 ESG 的投资者要求 SEC 阻止 JBS 在美国上市</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-02/esg-focused-investors-ask-sec-to-block-jbs-s-listing-in-us</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一群关注 ESG 的投资者要求美国监管机构拒绝为 JBS SA 提供在纽约交易股票的途径，原因是这家巴西肉类公司未能正确披露其对环境的影响。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-02/esg-focused-investors-ask-sec-to-block-jbs-s-listing-in-us</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 02 Oct 2024 04:01:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
